text: Yulin Subdistrict () is a subdistrict in Xinchang County, Zhejiang, China. , it has one residential community, 42 villages, and one water reservoir community under its administration. == See also == * List of township-level divisions of Zhejiang == References == Category:Township-level divisions of Zhejiang Category:Xinchang County
title: Yulin Subdistrict, Xinchang County
